      <li parentName="ol"><strong parentName="li">{`Performance`}</strong>{` improved quite a lot with the new code of the web application I built. I was replacing an old portal that was made in AngularJS. I decided to use TypeScript, Redux and React. I built an open source project to handle the fetching of data called `}<a parentName="li" {...{
